                     <interp inst="t18190217-29-defend305" type="age" value="36"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was indicted for that <rs id="t18190217-29-off174" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18190217-29-off174" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190217-29-off174" type="offenceSubcategory" value="bankrupcy"></interp>
               he, on the <rs id="t18190217-29-cd175" type="crimeDate">15th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190217-29-off174 t18190217-29-cd175"></join>, having had a commission of bankruptcy awarded and issued against him, directed to 
                     <persName id="t18190217-29-person306">
                        Henry 
                        Revell
